<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ de guó dù shì yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn 迦南834</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ de guó dù shì yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn, nǐ de zhèng quán shì yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn.
 nǐ de cí ài shì yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn, wǒ men yào xiàng nǐ huān hū.
 zūn guì róng yào dōu shǔ yú nǐ, quán néng yǒng yuǎn dōu shǔ yú nǐ.
 róng yào yǒng yuǎn dōu shǔ yú nǐ, zuò bǎo zuò de gāo yáng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>834</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>